@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vfqsdy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos((v1 + 0.66 * v2 + 0.04)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(0.20) + ((tmp + 0.66 / v1 + 0.69) * v2))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v2 + 0.79 + tmp + 0.40)))
    data[tid] = v0
